<H3> <TI>   Baena Soares Cited on Cuba Rejoining OAS </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Baena Soares Cited on Cuba Rejoining OAS </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   PA0806045794 Havana Radio Havana Cuba in Spanish 0000 GMT 7 
Jun 94 </F>

